name: Cepot
description:
Wayang Golek is a global masterpiece as well as an Indonesian intangible cultural heritage.

Astrajingga or known as Cepot is one of several Wayang Golek figures. Cepot is Semar's adopted son. His speech is childish but always full of meaning and advice.
